      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 offers a pure mechanical connection, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically sound, with a recently serviced dual-VANOS system ensuring optimal cam phasing and a reinforced rear subframe for enhanced torsional rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. Riding on a well-sorted suspension with refreshed bushings, it delivers the precise, communicative steering the chassis is known for. A driver-focused machine that balances raw performance with daily usability.",
